ewest first)\n- Categories from tags (reads `taxonomy-tags` from `ctx.data`)\n- Handles files without dates (omits `<pubDate>` tag)\n- All URLs use `config.baseUrl`\n\n---\n\n#### **Plugin 6: search-index** (DEPENDS: markdown-ext, syntax-highlight)\n**File:** `/workspace/tests/plugins/search-index.test.ts` - 8 tests\n\n**Requirements:**\n- `createSearchIndexPlugin()` factory function\n- Hook: `afterBuild`\n- Generates `search-index.json` with searchable content\n- **Format:**\n  ```json\n  [\n    {\n      \"slug\": \"post-1\",\n      \"title\": \"Post 1\",\n      \"content\": \"Plain text without HTML tags\",\n      \"tags\": [\"js\", \"web\"]\n    }\n  ]\n  ```\n- HTML tags stripped from content (plain text only)\n- Code blocks included in content\n- Tags included if present\n- Valid JSON array\n- Handles empty file list (empty array)\n\n---\n\n#### **Plugin 7: sitemap** (DEPENDS: taxonomy, rss-feed)\n**File:** `/workspace/tests/plugins/sitemap.test.ts` - 8 tests\n\n**Requirements:**\n- `createSitemapPlugin()` factory function\n- Hook: `afterBuild`\n- Generates `sitemap.xml` with all discoverable URLs\n- **Structure:**\n  ```xml\n  <?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n  <urlset xmlns=\"http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9\">\n    <url>\n      <loc>{config.baseUrl}/path.html</loc>\n    </url>\n  </urlset>\n  ```\n- Includes all entries from `ctx.output` map (content pages)\n- Includes all tag pages from `taxonomy-tags` in `ctx.data`\n- Includes `feed.xml` if present in output\n- Uses `config.baseUrl` for all URLs\n- Valid XML structure\n\n---\n\n#### **Plugin 8: dev-server** (DEPENDS: asset-pipeline, search-index)\n**File:** `/workspace/tests/plugins/dev-server.test.ts` - 7 tests\n\n**Requirements:**\n- `createDevServerPlugin()` factory function\n- Hook: `afterBuild`\n- Generates dev server configuration\n- **Config Structure:**\n  ```typescript\n  {\n    port: number;                           // Default: 3000\n    routes: Array<{ path: string; handler: string }>;\n    